channel.title: Hi Fellow RSPS Coders
channel.description:
Hi, i did everything i added a new rule to my firewall, and added my no-ip's to my GUI.java and server.java. and port forward my router "belkin". well i gave my friend the client and he connected. then after Disconnected us of the server. now every time i log in my server my self. here is what it says..
Loaded WorldMap In (68 ms)... Your server is now online. Connection from "and here is my no-ip" [client-1-Angel]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 1 ms] [client-1-Angel]: Invalid Server: "and here again is my no-ip"
I erased my no-ip just encase since im new to coding a bit, im not sure what's safe and not safe.
